            "title": "A股周五報跌    滬股全周升逾2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股向下，但一周計滬股升逾2%，深股升逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250206_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全日跌4點或0.12%，報3635點，今早開報3634，跌5點或0.14%，低見3625點，跌14點或0.38%，即反覆向上，最高見3645點，升6點或0.16%，午後窄幅，不超過上午波幅，成交7135.7億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指全日跌29點或0.26%，今早開報11136，跌57點或0.19%，最低見11108，跌49點或0.44%，午後見11184，升27點或0.24%，全日成交9966.57億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日跌9點或0.24%，報4104點，今早開報4019，跌5點或0.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數全日跌8點或0.38%，報2333點，今早開報2338，跌5點或0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指全周升78點或2.19% ; 深成指一周升137點或1.25%。</p>\n</div>",
